Code Assistant Using CodeLlama with LLAMA2 Large Language Model and Gradio

Overview
This project is an interactive code assistant application that leverages the CodeLlama model from LLAMA2 to provide intelligent programming assistance. The application is built using Gradio, which offers a user-friendly interface for seamless interaction.
The Code Assistant allows users to input prompts and receive code-related responses, including code generation, completion, and debugging help. The application features a dark theme for better readability and a modern look.

Features
Interactive Code Assistance: Utilize the CodeLlama model to assist with various programming tasks.
Gradio Interface: Easy-to-use web interface built with Gradio for interaction with the CodeLlama model.

Prerequisites
Ensure you have the following installed:
Python 3.7 or higher
requests library
gradio library
langchain
ollama
